# Entries in this file will not be synchronized in git

# ============================
# ==== general gitignores ====
# ============================
# python cache folders:
__pycache__
# shortcuts in root folder:
/*.lnk
# whitelist shorcut generator shortcut:
!_RUN BEFORE FIRST START AND AFTER FOLDER MOVE TO GENERATE SHORTCUTS.lnk
# log files:
log*.txt
# temporary id files for no-terminal start:
*.pid
# generated Python distro and packages:
/code/py_env/
# whitelist indicator file:
!/code/py_env/_USE developer_tools FOLDER (IN PARENT FOLDER) TO CHANGE PACKAGES_
# output files of developer tools:
/code/developer_tools/*.txt
# whitelist specific files in developer tools folder:
!/code/developer_tools/_README_.txt
!/code/developer_tools/_DEFAULT_PYHON_PACKAGES_.txt
# ===================================================

# =============================
# ==== specific gitignores ====
# =============================

